{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a0adcb3efb","title":"关于宗派主义问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0f4c01fc15","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"a0adcb3efb"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1fd5581b9a","type":"title","text":"关于宗派主义问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"a0adcb3efb"},{"id":"f173a1ae60","type":"paragraph","text":"凡是闹宗派主义、小团体主义的，最后都是搞不成的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"a0adcb3efb"}],"page":{"id":"4a5b8086ca","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"a0adcb3efb","start":347,"end":347}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"22526da7e4","type":"paragraph","text":"给中国人民解放军北京卫戍区二月十八日写的两个报告的批示（一九六七年二月十九日）","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a0adcb3efb"},{"id":"2711982e2d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东一九六七年二月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a0adcb3efb"},{"id":"34082b323e","type":"paragraph","text":"凡是闹宗派主义、小团体主义的，最后都是搞不成的。（陈伯达同志传达）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a0adcb3efb"},{"id":"3ee46eb71e","type":"title","text":"关于宗派主义问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a0adcb3efb"},{"id":"b5292f79f9","type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民解放军北京卫戍区二月十八日写了两个报告，一个是《关于五所高等院校短期军政训练试点的报告》，一个是《关于两个中学军政训练试点工作总结报告》，毛主席的批示如下：林彪同志：一、此两件应即转发全国；二、大学、中学和小学高年级每年训练一次，每次二十天，上课以后，在军训的二十天中，军训时间每天不要超过四小时，同时学校原课程每天相应减少四小时；三、党政军民机关除老年外，中年、青年都要实行军训，每年二十天。以上请酌办。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a0adcb3efb"}],"page":{"id":"e8c959e586","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a0adcb3efb","start":562,"end":563}}}},"__N_SSG":true}